parameters: \n<Ameria>"Nyaa!? What's wrong? Why are you shouting like that...?"
\n<Ameria>"Wh-What's the matter? Why are you shouting like that...?"

\n<Roselitte>"...What are you doing? Is it really okay for you to be
awake?"
\n<Ameria>"Eh? Oh... I'm sorry, it seems I've caused you to worry."
Ameria giggled "ehehe" and scratched her head.

\n<Ameria>"It seems my body was shocked from using too much magic.
It's like anemia, but I'm totally fine. I've had a doctor
look at me too."

\n<Ameria>"Right now, I'm also tending to the injured. Roselitte-san,
are you okay yourself?"
\n<Roselitte>"...I'm glad. I'm fine. It's good to see you're energetic."
Roselitte hit Lyric on the head.
\n<Lyric>"Ouch----! What are you doing all of a sudden!?"

\n<Roselitte>"I rushed over here thinking something had happened! There
are good lies and bad lies!"

\n<Lyric>"I didn't tell any lies! You just misunderstood on your own,
you silly knight!"

\n<Ameria>"Hey, both of you! This is a hospital room, so please don't
make too much noise!"

\n<Lyric>"Heheh. Like I'd let you hit me that many times. Retreat,
retreat...♪"
\n<Roselitte>"...You live with her all the time, don't you get tired?"

\n<Ameria>"Ahaha. But Roselitte-san, you seem like you'd get along
with her."
\n<Roselitte>"Please stop. I wouldn't last if I had to deal with her."
\n<Ameria>"Roselitte-san. So, what will you do now?"

\n<Roselitte>"...I haven't decided on anything specific yet. However, I
plan to gather my thoughts by tonight and depart tomorrow
morning."

\n<Roselitte>"It's appreciated that you're tending to the injured, but
please do so in moderation and prepare for tomorrow. It will
be quite a hassle if you collapse again."

\n<Roselitte>"Accommodations have been prepared for us. I'll come to call
on you later, and we can discuss tomorrow's plans then."
Roselitte gently placed her hand on Ameria's head.

\n<Roselitte>"Thanks to all of you, both myself and this town have been
saved."

\n<Roselitte>"On behalf of the empire, I express my gratitude. And thank
you for our fateful encounter.--Hallelujah."
\n<Injured person A>"The wound I got from the monster is... ughhh...!"

\n<Ameria>"Let me see. Ah... yes. It's okay, it's okay. It'll get
better soon, so don't worry."

\n<Injured person A>"Ah... amazing, it feels better... I'm glad we have such a
skilled healer here... truly saved me..."

\n<Ameria>"--Ehehe...♪ If anything else comes up, call me right away,
okay?♪"

\n<Injured person B>"Ameria-chan. Could you look at my wound too? The pain has
come back..."
\n<Injured person C>"Me too, after that would be fine."

\n<Ameria>"Yes!♪ I'll check on everyone in turn, so please wait a
little♪"
\n<Lyric>"Here, go ahead. You can pat my head too, if you like?"
Roselitte flicked Lyric's head with her finger.

\n<Roselitte>"Don't get carried away... Make sure Ameria doesn't overdo
it."
